<varlistentry id="options.SideUnfocusedBevel">
	<term>SideUnfocusedBevel <emphasis remap='I'>Bottom|Extra|NoInline|NoOutline|none|Left|Right|Top</emphasis></term>
	<listitem>
		<para>Sets the bevel of the window s frame sides while window is in unfocused state.</para>
		<para>If this is not used, values set with SideBevel will be used.</para>
		<para>See Also: <ulink url="Bevel#synopsis">Bevel flags</ulink> for further details.</para>
	</listitem>
</varlistentry>
